@startuml sequencia-resolver-ALVO
title Resolver — estado ALVO (Fase 3 fix)\nRetry-with-next-candidate: quando fill/click rejeita,\nexecutor pede próximo candidate ao resolver antes de escalar para healing.

skinparam BackgroundColor #F0FDF4
skinparam SequenceGroupBackgroundColor #DCFCE7

actor "test_*.py" as TEST
participant "step.fill()\nruntime/step.py" as STEP
participant "StepExecutor\n(NOVO wrapper)" as EXEC
participant "LocatorResolver\nresolver.py" as RES
participant "Page (Playwright)" as PAGE
participant "Locator" as LOC
participant "SQLite Catalog" as SQL
participant "Healing\nL2/L3" as HEAL

TEST -> STEP: step.fill(page, intent="Renda mensal",\n  value="1000", candidates_file=...)
activate STEP
STEP -> EXEC: execute_fill(intent, candidates, value)
activate EXEC

EXEC -> EXEC: exclude_indices = set()

loop retry chain (até candidates esgotarem ou execute OK)
  EXEC -> RES: resolve(intent, candidates,\n  action="fill", exclude=exclude_indices)
  activate RES

  alt L0a in-memory winning_idx_cache
    RES -> RES: idx = winning_idx_cache[intent]
    note right of RES #DCFCE7
      ⚡ Cache promove candidate vencedor
      da última execução para prioridade máxima.
      Speedup steps subsequentes.
    end note
    RES -> PAGE: build(candidates[idx])
    PAGE --> RES: locator
    RES --> EXEC: ResolveResult(locator, idx, level="L0_promoted")
  else L1 candidates walk
    loop for idx, c in enumerate(candidates) if idx ∉ exclude
      RES -> PAGE: build(c)
      PAGE --> RES: locator
      RES -> LOC: _exists(locator) = count() > 0
      alt existe
        LOC --> RES: True
        RES --> EXEC: ResolveResult(locator, idx)
        break
      else não existe
        LOC --> RES: False
      end
    end
    alt nenhum candidate resolve
      RES --> EXEC: raise LocatorNotFoundError
    end
  end
  deactivate RES

  EXEC -> PAGE: locator.fill(value, timeout=1500)
  alt fill EXECUTA (OK)
    PAGE --> EXEC: sucesso
    EXEC -> RES: promote_cache(intent, idx)
    RES -> RES: winning_idx_cache[intent] = idx
    RES -> SQL: record_success(intent, candidates[idx])
    note right of RES #DCFCE7
      ✅ Só persiste após EXECUÇÃO OK.
      Recipe catalog aprende fix real.
    end note
    EXEC --> STEP: StepResult(passed=True,\n  winning_idx=idx,\n  attempted_indices=[...])
    break
  else fill REJEITA
    PAGE --> EXEC: TimeoutError / ElementInterceptedError
    EXEC -> EXEC: exclude_indices.add(idx)
    note right of EXEC #DCFCE7
      🔁 GAP-01 fix: adiciona idx à exclude,
      volta ao topo do loop, resolver pega
      próximo candidate elegível.
    end note
    alt exclude_indices == set(range(len(candidates)))
      EXEC -> HEAL: escalate(step, all_indices_failed)
      HEAL --> EXEC: healed OR unresolved
      EXEC --> STEP: StepResult(...)
      break
    end
  end
end

deactivate EXEC
deactivate STEP
STEP --> TEST: passed / rejected

legend right #D1FAE5
  <b>Contrato do fix (Fase 3)</b>:
  1. LocatorResolver.resolve() aceita `exclude_indices: set[int]`.
  2. StepExecutor (novo/estendido) wrapping: resolve → execute → retry se falha.
  3. Cache in-memory `winning_idx_cache: dict[intent_hash, int]`.
  4. `record_success` só após execução confirmada, não após existência.
  5. Escalação para healing SOMENTE quando todos candidates esgotaram.

  <b>Regressão testável</b>:
  tests/regression/resolver/test_gap01_first_candidate_exists_but_fill_fails.py
  Pré-fix: FALHA. Pós-fix: PASSA.
end legend

@enduml
